content.rendered:
Compressor nebuliser is suitable for the successful treatment of allergies, asthma and many other respiratory disorders.

 

Featuring a contemporaneity style and soft, pleasing pastel colors, the Nebuliser was created with pediatric environments in mind, yet is also perfect for adult applications as well. Because children often become fearful with the use of regular-style nebulisers, this model has received a great deal of praise for a friendly design.

Max flow rate 8 L/min
Maximum nebulization rate ≥0.35 mL/min
MMAD 4 microns
Sound level ≤65 dB
